{"name": "seismod1d", "metadata": {"name": "seismod1d", "version": "0.3.5", "classifiers": ["Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": "https://github.com/equinor/seismod1d", "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["numpy", "pandas", "matplotlib", "scipy", "lasio", "segyio", "scikit-learn"], "summary": "Create synthetic seismic", "upload_time": 1733128182}, "documentation": ["\nCreate synthetic seismic\n\n\n"], "modules": [{"name": "seismod1d.utils", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "seismod1d.utils.generate_test_model", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "model_version", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Generates a test model for synthmod 1d\n\nParameters\n----------\nmodel_version : int, optional\n    Model version, by default 1\n\nReturns\n-------\nTuple[np.ndarray]\n    depth, vp, vs, rhob, delta, epsilon, gamma"]}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "seismod1d.cmap", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "seismod1d.cmap.get_colormap", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "cmap_name", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "reverse", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "seismod1d.wavelet", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "seismod1d.wavelet.get_wavelet", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "wav_duration", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "wav_dt", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "wav_type", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "wav_parameters", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "seismod1d.wavelet.time_to_frequency", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "wav_time", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "wav_amplitude", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "crop_positive", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "seismod1d.wavelet._get_time", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "duration", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "dt", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Make a time vector.\n\nThe time vector will have an odd number of samples,\nand will be symmetric about 0."]}, {"name": "seismod1d.wavelet._ricker", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "duration", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "dt", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "f", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Also known as the mexican hat wavelet, models the function:\n\n$$\nA =  (1 - 2 \\pi^2 f^2 t^2) e^{-\\pi^2 f^2 t^2}\n$$\n\n```\n.. plot::\n\n    import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n    w, t = _ricker(0.256, 0.002, 40)\n    plt.plot(t, w)\n```\n\nArgs:\n\n: duration (float): The length in seconds of the wavelet.\n  dt (float): The sample interval in seconds (often one of 0.001, 0.002,\n\n  > or 0.004).\n\n  f (float): Centre frequency of the wavelet in Hz.\n\nReturns:\n\n: ndarray: A vector containing a tuple of (wavelet, t) is returned.\n"]}, {"name": "seismod1d.wavelet._ormsby", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "duration", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "dt", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "f", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["The Ormsby wavelet requires four frequencies which together define a\ntrapezoid shape in the spectrum. The Ormsby wavelet has several sidelobes,\nunlike Ricker wavelets.\n\n```\n.. plot::\n\n    import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n    w, t = _ormsby(0.256, 0.002, [5, 10, 40, 80])\n    plt.plot(t, w)\n```\n\nArgs:\n\n: duration (float): The length in seconds of the wavelet.\n  dt (float): The sample interval in seconds (usually 0.001, 0.002,\n\n  > or 0.004).\n\n  f (array-like): A tuple of frequencies (f1, f2, f3, f4).\n\nReturns:\n\n: ndarray: A vector containing a tuple of (wavelet, t) is returned.\n"]}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "seismod1d", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "seismod1d.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "seismod1d.td", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "seismod1d.td.get_time", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "zz", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "vp", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "start_time", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "seismod1d.td.get_time_linear", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "zz", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "vp", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "seismod1d.td.get_time_from_td", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "z_td", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "t_td", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "z_in", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "kind", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "int_method", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "seismod1d.td.get_depth_from_td", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "z_td", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "t_td", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "t_in", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "kind", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "int_method", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "seismod1d.td.apply_td_stretch", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "ref_time", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "model_depth", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "model_time", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "td_depth", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "td_time", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "direction", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []